# cargo-cicd-verify project ontology — deliberately empty of individuals.
#
# cargo-cicd-pack's own ontology.ttl (packs/cargo-cicd-pack/ontology.ttl) is
# a complete, source-audited model of ~/cargo-cicd's real command surface;
# this consumer adds no project-specific facts on top of it (unlike
# receiptctl/schema/domain.ttl, which unions in project-specific
# cnv:Command individuals for clap-noun-verb-pack). This file exists only
# to satisfy `[ontology] source` in ggen.toml — the real domain facts come
# entirely from the wired pack.

@prefix cnv: <http://seanchatmangpt.github.io/packs/clap-noun-verb#> .
@prefix cc:  <http://seanchatmangpt.github.io/packs/cargo-cicd#> .
@prefix rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
